        "subject": "LU-11666 tests: disable sanity tests 130[a-e] for ARM",
        "message": "LU-11666 tests: disable sanity tests 130[a-e] for ARM\n\nSanity tests 130a, 130b, 130c, 130d and 130e are consistently\nfailing on ARM clients. This patch adds them to ALWAYS_EXCEPT\nlist to exclude the failures.\n\nThey will be removed from the list and re-enabled in the patch\nthat fixes the failures.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nChange-Id: Ib3135ac438db839f862d34369f434ae1c84ecad5\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\n"
